---
title: "US28 — Browse expert categories"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertsScreen (category chips)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>BrowseExperts
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertCategory
  A->>B: tap a category chip
  B->>C: filter(categoryId)
  C->>E: categories + filtered experts
  E-->>C: filtered set
  C-->>B: filtered list
  B-->>A: experts for that specialty
  note over E: read via SupabaseGateway
